1.00	Tomorrow_(Elva_Hsiao_album)	Tomorrow (Elva Hsiao album)	Tomorrow is Taiwanese Mandopop artist Elva Hsiao's (Chinese: ) third Mandarin studio album. It was released on 21 April 2001 by Virgin Records Taiwan, a sub-label of EMI Music Taiwan. The album was released with a VCD containing highlight footage of Hsiao's Summer Rose Concert Spectacular in August 2000. The music video for "下一次戀愛" (Next Love) features Taiwanese actor Joseph Chang.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/b7/Elva_Hsiao-Tomorrow-cover.jpg/220px-Elva_Hsiao-Tomorrow-cover.jpg
